results.description:
After learning of the danger posed by the Time Twisters, a trio of
destructive beings from the far-flung future, Thor and his companions agree
to accompany Zarrko the Tomorrow Man on his quest to end their threat before
his world is destroyed. But can a villain from the Thunder God's past be
trusted, especially with the stakes so high? Accompany Thor, the Warriors
Three and the ever-lovely Jane Foster on this time-twisted tale of a
tomorrow that may never come!

results.title: Thor (1966) #245
results.description: With the world in ruins, Thor and his companions - along with the Tomorrow Man and his Servitor - make a last-ditch effort to save the fate of not only Zarrko's world, but also that of all worlds. But will even a trip to the end of time be enough to stop the awesome chain of events that threatens every living being? The Thunder God is faced with challenges unlike any seen before in this, the ultimate chapter of the Saga of the Time Twisters!
